    <item>
      <title>中国正在为俄罗斯建造和测试致命攻击无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情的欧洲官员称，中国和俄罗斯公司正在研发一种类似于伊朗部署在乌克兰的攻击无人机，这一迹象表明北京方面可能正接近提供西方官员警告的那种致命援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:42:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>帕克称，拜登在泄露的民主党民意调查备忘录中支持率暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-plummets-in-leaked-democratic-polling-memo-puck-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据新闻网站 Puck 周二发布的一份民意调查泄露备忘录显示，总统乔·拜登在上周的辩论中表现出色后，支持率暴跌，出现近三年来“最大的单周跌幅”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-plummets-in-leaked-democratic-polling-memo-puck-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:23:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗寻求与美国进行新谈判，委内瑞拉欢迎俄罗斯军舰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/venezuela-welcomes-russian-warship-as-maduro-seeks-new-us-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在尼古拉斯·马杜罗宣布其政府与美国在本月总统大选前重启谈判数小时后，一艘俄罗斯军舰抵达委内瑞拉海岸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/venezuela-welcomes-russian-warship-as-maduro-seeks-new-us-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:36:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普一季度筹资 3.31 亿美元，超过拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/trump-raises-331-million-in-quarter-as-war-chest-now-tops-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在第二季度筹集了 3.31 亿美元，这笔筹款使他手头的现金比总统乔·拜登还多，这一发展可能会加剧民主党对现任总统竞选活动的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/trump-raises-331-million-in-quarter-as-war-chest-now-tops-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:32:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登政府官员称医院必须提供紧急堕胎服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-officials-tell-doctors-emergency-abortions-are-legal-duty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府周二告诉医院和医疗保健提供者，他们有法律义务为遇到医疗紧急情况的孕妇实施堕胎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-officials-tell-doctors-emergency-abortions-are-legal-duty</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:28:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普纽约宣判因豁免权被推迟至 9 月 18 日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/trump-sentencing-rescheduled-for-sept-18-court-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的纽约封口费案的宣判被推迟两个月至 9 月 18 日，以便法官能够审查美国最高法院有关总统豁免权的里程碑式裁决的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/trump-sentencing-rescheduled-for-sept-18-court-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 18:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
